<br>
<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>After much discussion, we have decided that ezSupporters will NOT see the new ads that come from the FREE GOLD promotion. <br>
<br>
In the near future, ezSupporters may have the option of seeing the sponsorships in exchange for extending their own ezSupporter subscriptions.<br>
<br>
The reason we are changing our policy is because we want as many communities as possible to take advantage of this great opportunity. Some communities were concerned about the effect it would have on their ezSupporter members and were reluctant to try the program. <br>
<br>
Even though we still disagree, we can also understand the position expressed by some members regarding our no-ad policy for ezSupporters. Admins will still be able to put their own ads on the boards and will be seen by everyone. This has always been the case and will continue. I guess in the end we felt perception/customer satisfaction was more important than contractual facts. <br>
<br>
We hope that enough communities will participate and our sponsors will be satisfied with their investments so that we can continue to offer an ad-supported (non popup) product. You can help by encouraging your community to participate and also clicking on the sponsors. If the trial is a success, ezboard will be able to offer a non-pop up, ad-supported product, something we have not been able to do in YEARS.<br>
<br>
Thanks for your feedback and continued support.<br>
<br>
Now, let's move forward and make sure this trial is a complete success. <hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
<br>
That being said, I am going to process our &quot;Free Gold&quot; membership.  In short, this means:<br>
<br>
Still no language filter (I know some of you will love this!)<br>
Text only advertisements (No pop-ups)<br>
